              Getting 100 levels in two weeks is really easy now and in my opinion the whole game is now worthless. I wonder why the hell I played for over a year to get over 100th level when you can do it in a week or two now. I don't see any point to T4C anymore now. I think every server is a total and complete wash now, I just want to know what drugs Vircom was smoking when they allowed this? I don't see how a server plans on keeping players when they can get 100 levels a week and even if they do make a fix the damage has been done! The only solution would be to fix the insane amount of exp being given out and have every server do a complete wipe, anything less is a joke.<br><br>I quit T4C about a week ago and I have since discovered Everquest, while it does have its own problems I know I don't have to worry about this kinda crap, levels actually have meaning.  I am totally disgusted by the current state of T4C and its level a min atmosphere it now has and I'm pissed off that I wasted over a year of my time playing this damn game when a newbie can now do it in a week. Thanks for the total slap in the face.<br><br>
